***Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course is for practicing knowledge and skills acquired during the study at the university in working environment outside of Estonia.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After passing the course student After successful completion of the practice the student: (1) have gained practical work experience outside of Estonia; (2) is able to work in a team; (3) is able to adapt to the daily work routines; (4) has an overview of a particular institution/company, its operating environment, market potential, career opportunities in this institution, as well as institution-specific practical aspects of corporate governance; (5) is able to give a report about his/her activities in the company: problem setup, goals of the training, specific task of the trainee, the results of work; (6) is able to analyze what it is in the university lessons learned from makes practical use to him/her, which has benefited and what would be necessary to modify or customize in the learning process; (7) is able to analyze how the institution/company gained the experience and knowledge has furthered his education in the university; (8) is able to do periodic self-reflection of how the objectives set have been completed and is able to set new goals for the next reflection period.
